id: pm-drje
title: "GitHub #21: document resilient global git-install recovery"
description: "Document and remediate GitHub issue #21: npm global install from the GitHub repository can fail with ENOTEMPTY and leave a broken pm symlink on reinstall."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 1
